description: The latest job applicant I banged was quite interesting. He used to work as a car repairman but his employer got into trouble so our boy spent some time working abroad. He would have stayed there for good but his girlfriend convinced him to come back. They broke up in the end so it wasn't a good decision. To my surprise, he worked as a bouncer and really liked it. The guy did kickboxing a lot and got involved in some serious fights. Working as muscles was his hobby. Fortunately, it wasn't paid well so the boy came to our agency for help. I was ready to give him a job of his dreams because I really wanted to have fun today. When I was done with the man, he just lied on the floor fucked up and sweaty. The little whore loved it and promised to see me again if he ever needs a new job.
title: Dirty Scout 200
